#5300
Near Death Trap Fall - 5307~
2 g 100
~
* Near Death Trap stuns actor
wait 2 sec
set stunned %actor.hitp%
%damage% %actor% %stunned%
wait 2 sec
%send% %actor% You somehow survive the fall.
~
